                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9595" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1439</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1244 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">铩羽而归：八马茶业上市之路漫漫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Returning home: The road to the listing of the Bama Tea is long</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汤新华，曾露露，李婷婷，黄昕宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">八马茶业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">八马茶业；IPO；茶行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bama Tea; IPO; Tea industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">茶是中国人日常生活中不可缺少的元素之一，但到了资本市场，茶企却不受欢迎，至今没有茶企登上A股市场。过去的十多年间，不少被寄予厚望的茶企，都偃旗息鼓。八马茶业作为茶行业中的佼佼者，十年三次冲击IPO，从中小板到创业板，从创业板再到主板，都以失败告终，让人不禁思考：为什么对于茶企而言，A股上市会如此艰难？本案例通过展示八马茶业的基本情况、三次IPO失败事件，介绍茶行业、八马茶业自身的商业模式、会计合规、关联交易及信息披露等情况，引导学生了解A股上市条件的内容和要求，引发学生对茶行业公司上市困境的思考，同时希望能对想要通过IPO上市的茶企提供一定的经验启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Tea is one of the indispensable elements in the daily life of Chinese, but when it comes to the capital market, tea companies are not popular, and no tea companies have been listed on the A-share market. In the past ten years, many tea companies with high hopes have died down. As a leader in the tea industry, Bama Tea has hit the IPO three times in ten years, from the small and medium-sized board to the GEM, from the GEM to the main board, it has ended in failure, which makes people think: why is it so difficult for tea companies to list on the A-share market? This case shows the basic situation of the Bama tea, the three IPO failures, and introduces the tea industry, Bama Tea&#39;s own business model, accounting compliance, related party transactions and information disclosure, etc., guides students to understand the content and requirements of A-share listing conditions, triggers students&#39; thinking about the listing dilemma of tea industry companies, and hopes to provide some experience enlightenment for tea companies that want to go public through IPO.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">主板、中小板、创业板上市条件对比;金融市场理论;加盟模式;风险管理理论;新收入准则;总额法和净额法:主要责任人、代理人的判断;关联交易界定;IPO企业财务规范的概念和具体要求;注册制改革;信号理论;标准化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
